snippet.title: Gravity Error
snippet.description:
Are you skilled enough to guide Force in his quest seeking emotional stableness?
Gravity Error is an 2D puzzle/platformer about changing gravity. Guide Force in his quest seeking emotional stableness in a set of levels and avoid being crushed. Solve the puzzles in multiple creative ways.

Coming soon to PS4 and Xbox One.

http://www.semaphorelab.com
